# Group Meetings Calendar

Represents meetings calendar information.

---

**Meetings Calendar Attributes:**
- events: `(Array<Calendar Event Object>)` : List of event information, **Required**

**Calendar Event Attributes:**
- id `(String)` : Event's unique ID, **Required**
- start `(String)` : Event's start date, **Required**
- end `(String)` : Event's end date, **Required**
- allDay `(Boolean)` : Whether event is all day 
- title `(String)` : Event's title, **Required**
- data `(Data Object)` : Event's further information

**Data Object:**
- eventId `(String)` : Event's unique ID, **Required**, ***Event Reference***
- organization `(String)` : Event's organization's ID, **Required**, ***Organization Reference***
- name `(String)` : Event's name, **Required**
- eventType `(String)` : Event's type, **Required**

## Meetings Calendars [/{schoolId}/meetingsCalendar]

### Get Meetings Calendar [GET /{schoolId}/meetingsCalendar/{calendarType}]

+ Parameters

    + schoolId (required) - school id
    + calendarType (required) - type of calendar to return

+ Request (application/json)

    + Headers

            Accept: application/json

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    Successfully returned meetings calendar

    + Body
    
            {
                "events": [
                    {
                      "id": "<id>",
                      "start": "2019-09-03",
                      "end": "2019-09-03",
                      "allDay": true,
                      "title": "Event Title",
                      "data": {
                        "eventId": "<eventId>",
                        "name": "Event Name",
                        "organization": "<organizationId>",
                        "eventType": "Community"
                      }
                    }
                ]
            }
            
+ Response 400 (application/json)

    Bad Request

    + Body

+ Response 403 (application/json)

    Forbidden

    + Body

## Meetings [/{schoolId}/meetings]

### Get Meetings [GET /{schoolId}/meetings{?startDate,endDate}]

+ Parameters

    + schoolId (required) - school id
    + startDate (optional) - match meetings starting on or after this date, in ISO 8601 format, such as 2023-09-01
    + endDate (optional) - match meetings starting before or on this date, in ISO 8601 format, such as 2023-09-30

+ Request (application/json)

    + Headers

            Accept: application/json

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    Successfully returned meetings matching date range

    + Body
    
            {
                "<id>": {
                    "endDate": "2023-09-14",
                    "endTime": 900,
                    "eventId": "<eventId>",
                    "featured": null,
                    "hidden": null,
                    "id": "<id>",
                    "private": null,
                    "public": null,
                    "resources": [],
                    "startDate": "2023-09-14",
                    "startTime": 800,
                    "status": "Confirmed",
                    "eventData": {
                        "attachments": [],
                        "contacts": [],
                        "description": "Event Description",
                        "id": "<eventId>",
                        "name": "Event Name",
                        "organization": "<organizationId>",
                        "status": "Confirmed",
                        "type": "Event Type",
                        "version": 2
                    }
                }
            }
            
+ Response 400 (application/json)

    Bad Request

    + Body

+ Response 403 (application/json)

    Forbidden

    + Body

